  "prompt": "What are your favorite YouTube channels about Star Wars content?",
  "response": "There are many great YouTube channels dedicated to Star Wars content that cater to a variety of interests, from lore analysis to fandom discussions to gameplay. Here are some popular ones:\n\n1. **Star Wars Theory** - Focuses on theories, lore, and character analyses, often diving deep into the mythology of the Star Wars universe.\n\n2. **The Lore Master** - Specializes in detailed lore explanations, exploring the expanded universe and the deeper stories behind characters and events.\n\n3. **HelloGreedo** - Offers commentary on Star Wars films, game reviews, and a plethora of fan theories, all delivered with a humorous twist.\n\n4. **Screen Rant** - Has a dedicated section for Star Wars that includes breakdowns, news, and theories, presenting relatable and engaging content.\n\n5. **Star Wars Explained** - Provides concise explanations of various characters, lore, and events from the Star Wars universe, making it easy to understand complex storylines.\n\n6. **The Stupendous Wave** - Focuses on Star Wars news, commentary, and theories, often discussing upcoming projects and their potential impact on the franchise.\n\n7. **Game Theory (MatPat)** - While not exclusively Star Wars, MatPat often dives into Star Wars-related theories, especially in the context of the games.\n\n8. **Cosmic Wonder** - Covers Star Wars news, theories, and updates on upcoming projects, often with a focus on how it fits into the larger cinematic universe.\n\nThese channels offer a mix of entertainment, education, and deep dives into the beloved galaxy far, far away.",
